@EduShield.Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5000

### Health Check
GET {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/health
Accept: application/json

### Test Public Endpoint
GET {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/test/public
Accept: application/json

### Dev Authentication
POST {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/dev
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "techtonicwave.business@gmail.com"
}

### Google Authentication (requires Google ID token)
POST {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/auth/google
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "idToken": "your-google-id-token-here"
}

### Test Authenticated Endpoint (requires Bearer token)
GET {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/test/authenticated
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

