### Faculty Management Endpoints

### Create Faculty Member
POST {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/faculty
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "firstName": "John",
  "lastName": "Doe",
  "email": "john.doe@university.edu",
  "phoneNumber": "+1-555-123-4567",
  "dateOfBirth": "1985-03-15",
  "address": "123 University Ave, City, State 12345",
  "gender": 0,
  "department": "Computer Science",
  "subject": "Software Engineering",
  "hireDate": "2020-08-15"
}

### Get All Faculty Members
GET {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/faculty
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get Faculty by ID
GET {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/faculty/{{facultyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get Faculty by Email
GET {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/faculty/email/john.doe@university.edu
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get Faculty by Employee ID
GET {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/faculty/employee/faculty_001
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get Faculty by Department
GET {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/faculty/department/Computer%20Science
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get Faculty by Subject
GET {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/faculty/subject/Software%20Engineering
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Get Active Faculty Only
GET {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/faculty/active
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Update Faculty Member
PUT {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/faculty/{{facultyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "department": "Computer Engineering",
  "subject": "Computer Architecture",
  "isActive": true
}

### Check if Faculty Exists
GET {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/faculty/{{facultyId}}/exists
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Check if Email Exists
GET {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/faculty/email/john.doe@university.edu/exists
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Check if Employee ID Exists
GET {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/faculty/employee/faculty_001/exists
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Accept: application/json

### Delete Faculty Member
DELETE {{EduShield.Api_HostAddress}}/api/v1/faculty/{{facultyId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
